const ArrowCircleDown = forwardRef<SVGSVGElement, IconProps>((props, ref) => (
  <IconBase ref={ref} {...props} renderPath={renderPath} />
));

ArrowCircleDown.displayName = "ArrowCircleDown";

export default ArrowCircleDown;
